    <div class="tip-box">
      <span class="tip-box-ico">&#128161;</span>
      <p><strong>Key insight:</strong> The most effective melatonin-free sleep gummies address the underlying causes of poor sleep — magnesium deficiency, elevated cortisol, excessive neural excitability — rather than sedating you into unconsciousness. This is why they produce better long-term outcomes with fewer side effects, even though the initial effect may feel less dramatic than a 10mg melatonin dose.</p>
    </div>

