      <span class="warn-box-ico">&#9888;</span>
      <p><strong>Important:</strong> If you experience chronic insomnia lasting more than three months, frequent nighttime awakenings, or sleep disturbances that significantly impact daytime functioning, consult a sleep specialist. Non-hormonal sleep gummies are supplements, not treatments for clinical sleep disorders like obstructive sleep apnea or chronic insomnia. They work best as part of a comprehensive sleep hygiene protocol.</p>
